data.description:
**OWNER FINANCING AVAILABLE!**

Rent to Own / Lease to own! 

Gorgeous, modern and spacious house located right off route 60 and 53rd Avenue. This house is in the most convenient area of town, sitting right across Applebee's, Walmart, Dunkin Donuts, Tropical Smoothie and many more! Down the street you have stores such as the Indian River Shopping Mall, Publix, Bealls, Chic Fila, ABC Fine Wine and Spirits, Home Depot, Target and much much more! 
This home is 100% freshly renovated with a 4/2 structure and pool! Everything in the house has been fully renovated. New floor vinyl planking installed,  new upgraded appliances, such as fridge, stove, microwave and dishwasher. Brand new kitchen with new counter tops, cabinets, and hardware. Fresh new blinds, doors, windows and garage. Completely new and modern bathrooms, including toilet, tubs and cabinets. Upgraded light fixtures throughout. 
Enjoy a nice relaxing dip in the huge, eye-catching 7 1/2ft deep pool or enjoy the view by hanging in the screen back porch. 
On the corner of a large lot and private road with beautiful landscape. 
 Interested in making this your home, please contact 772-588-4469.
